description:
CODEX PRESENTS

The Incredible Adventures of Van Helsing II - Upd. v1.1.01c incl. DLC

Release Date :  8/2014                         Protection : Steam
Discs        :  1                              Genre      : RPG

For list of changes read included patchnotes.txt

- Extract
- Run setup.exe and install update to your gamedir
- Copy crack from CODEX folder to your installdir
- Play

Notes: This patch requires: CODEX release of Van Helsing II
This patch includes new DLC: Ink Hunt, also Bonus Pack DLC is
unlocked now as well. Previous update is not needed.

Block game exe in your firewall to prevent the game from trying to go
online
